Package al6utils

Provides utility classes for developing AnyLogic models.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Config An object that provides read access to configuration data.
 

Class Summary
AbstractConfig Skeletal implementation of the Config interface to ease the effort in implementing Config.
BooleanParser Utility class providing methods for creating booleans from other types.
ConfigJSON Implementation of the Config interface that takes its configuration data from a JSON-formatted text file.
DelimitedFileExporter Construct a data set that can be arranged as rows of fields and export it to a delimited text file.
DelimitedFileImporter Import the contents of a delimited text file and provide iterative access to the rows and name-based access to the fields.
Format Utility class providing methods involving text formats.
Math Utility class providing methods implementing math routines that are not available in java.lang.Math.
 

Package al6utils Description

Provides utility classes for developing AnyLogic models.
